+
+| Capability | Gate policy | Audit log | Executor wired | Runner dependency | Real integration | Rating |
+|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|
+| Merge | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ (GITHUB_TOKEN + allowlist) | ✅ Octokit | 🟢 Ready |
